to install:

1. have Spotify
2. (step about environment variables here)
3. create symlink to your app folder for spotify
  $ mkdir ~/Spotify
  $ ln -s path/to/hashtop40/app hashtop40
4. startup the node (NOTE: I'm using a nodeenv for local development https://github.com/ekalinin/nodeenv)
  (from the hashtop40 directory)
  $ node ./src/app.js
5. go to Spotify and search spotify:app:hashtop40
6. VOILA
